{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 72480, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "假设：喝水和死去都不花时间，", "timestamp": 1593666095, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72486, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "15分钟吗，二进制变成5进制而已", "timestamp": 1593666168, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72487, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一百万只", "timestamp": 1593666181, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72488, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不死，15分钟死，30分钟死，45分钟死，1小时死", "timestamp": 1593666192, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72496, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这是个信息论问题。log2(1000000)=19.93 算20，20/4=5。五只", "timestamp": 1593666287, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72502, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 5只是错的吧。。。", "timestamp": 1593666349, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72513, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 只能按 五进制理解吧，5只乘4有点扯。你这个思路岂不是300分钟只要1头猪呢？但这一头猪第一次喝完就死了，你告诉我是哪号水桶有毒？", "timestamp": 1593666496, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72519, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我想当然了……如果是限定15分钟那么20是对的。但1小时要考虑消耗问题", "timestamp": 1593666589, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72520, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 但是信息论可以用来证明是最优解", "timestamp": 1593666588, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72523, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 20也是错的。。。", "timestamp": 1593666599, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72524, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 哦，你说15分钟，那就对", "timestamp": 1593666621, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72560, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我来扮演一下小白!这是为什么啊?20只怎么做到的", "timestamp": 1593667103, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72573, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "log5(1000000)不应该是9只吗，如果毒水和普通水混合以后不论浓度都会死的话", "timestamp": 1593667420, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72595, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/60227816/answer/1274071217", "timestamp": 1593667819, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72624, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 对我刚也想说这不是知乎上的么", "timestamp": 1593668474, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72791, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 把这100w只猪分别编号0~999999，然后转化为二进制码，那么二进制码就有$[log_2 1000000]+1$位，然后取来相同数量的猪，第i只猪喝第i位是1的水$(i\\in[0,[log_2 1000000]])$即可", "timestamp": 1593672825, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72813, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我感觉应该是34只？\n首先应该是可以测4次（因为测量中间没有办法可以得到别的信息所以只能等着）\n如果给这些水编号的话就应该有100w种可能性\n如果每次都有n头猪喝水（所有水平均分）的话就会有n种情况，喝了四次之后n^4种情况，至少要比100w大才可以\n100w^0.25=31.6，所以应该是32，32，32，31，每次死一头之后别的猪可以重复利用所以应该是34头？", "timestamp": 1593673310, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 72878, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "2^（n+n-1+n-2+n-3）>10^6，n=7？", "timestamp": 1593674846, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 73443, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 12354, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 答案上面有了。。。9只", "timestamp": 1593688118, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 12354, "reply": 19, "tag": null, "text": "# 问：\n\n一百万桶水中一桶有毒，猪喝毒水后15内任意时刻死。至少要多少只猪才能一个小时内求出哪一桶有毒？\n\n请给出喝水方案并证明该方案为最优解。", "timestamp": 1593666032, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782589, "url": "", "vote": {}}}